<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فُصِّلَتْ}</span> ... بُيِّنَتْ بِالأَمْرِ وَالنَّهْيِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تُوبُوا}</span> ... ارْجِعُوا إِلَيْهِ نَادِمِينَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَثْنُونَ صُدُورَهُمْ}</span> ... يُضْمِرُونَ فِي صُدُورِهِمُ الكُفْرَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِيَسْتَخْفُوا مِنْهُ}</span> ... لِيَسْتَتِرُوا مِنَ اللهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَسْتَغْشُونَ ثِيَابَهُمْ}</span> ... يَتَغَطَّوْنَ بِثِيَابِهِمْ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُسْتَقَرَّهَا}</span> ... مَسْكَنَهَا فِي الدُّنْيَا، وَبَعْدَ المَوْتِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَمُسْتَوْدَعَهَا}</span> ... المَوْضِعَ الَّذِي تَمُوتُ فِيهِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِيَبْلُوَكُمْ}</span> ... لِيَخْتَبِرَكُمْ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أُمَّةٍ مَّعْدُودَةٍ}</span> ... أَجَلٍ مَعْلُومٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَا يَحْبِسُهُ}</span> ... مَا يَمْنَعُهُ؟<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَحَاقَ}</span> ... أَحَاطَ بِهِمْ مِنْ كُلِّ جَانِبٍ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَيَؤُوسٌ}</span> ... شَدِيدُ اليَاسِ وَالقُنُوطِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ضَرَّاءَ}</span> ... ضِيقٍ وَنَكْبَةٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{السَّيِّئَاتُ}</span> ... الضِّيقُ، وَالشَّدَائِدُ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَفَرِحٌ}</span> ... لبَطِرٌ بِالنِّعَمِ، مَغْرُورٌ بِهَا.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَخُورٌ}</span> ... مُبَالِغٌ فِي الفَخْرِ وَالتَّعَالِي عَلَى النَّاسِ.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>